Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.28,0:01:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.78,0:01:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.32,0:01:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好啦快來快來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.45,0:01:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.24,0:01:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快 一口氣吹完
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.24,0:01:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大早上就是蛋糕？！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.95,0:01:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an8}小紅 好吃嗎
